comments: Burks (DET) initiates contact with Siakam's (TOR) body, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Livers (DET) establishes himself in Achiuwa's (TOR) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Barnes (TOR) moves alongside Ivey's (DET) path and maintains a legal guarding position as incidental contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Livers (DET) establishes a wide screening position and illegal contact occurs with Barnes' (TOR) lower body that affects his ability to defend the pick.
Stewart (DET) and Young (TOR) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Young (TOR) establishes himself in Ivey's (DET) path and marginal contact occurs during the dribble-hand-off.
Ivey (DET) brings his lower body slightly forward and marginal leg to leg contact occurs with VanVleet (TOR) as he steps through during the pass.
Bogdanovic (DET) makes marginal contact with Achiuwa's (TOR) arm while defending the drive to the basket and shot attempt.
VanVleet (TOR) makes contact with Burks' (DET) elbow during his upward shooting motion.
Livers (DET) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Siakam (TOR) during the pass.
Livers (DET) initiates contact with VanVleet's (TOR) arm and affects his SQBR.
Achiuwa (TOR) makes clean contact with the ball, any additional contact to Bogdanovic's (DET) body while jumping is deemed incidental.
Livers (DET) deflects the ball and causes it to go out of bounds.
Bogdanovic (DET) commits a take foul on Achiuwa (TOR).
